subSubSection.paragraph:
but not from Martinique . This is the first record of this species from this island. This species seems to be rather rare on companion plants as it was collected in few numbers. It was also found in association with
T. evansi ( Moraes and McMurtry 1983 )
but probably an inefficient predator of that species. The biology of this species is totally unknown.
